==Damla't Talindo (Mission and Vision)==

Ikami, ing Komunidad a Tuturu ampong Pastoral ning Don Bosco Pampanga, akakit mi la reng kayanakan antimong taung kayanib antimong talasuyu-pekapun (servant-leaders) ning Pisamban da reng Pakakalulu.
<br>

Mangaku kaming
- iyuna la reng kayanakan a kalulu, melakuan, at atiu king panganib
- munie pamagaral a Cristianu at Catolicung pangkabilugan paglalawe (holistic) at piyagum (integral)
- munie matas a uri ning pamagaral busal ning Salesian Preventive System
- itanam karela ing lugud king pamilia, pamalenan/komunidad ampong bangsa
- makiugnayan kareng eganaganang magobra kareng kayanakan
- tairan la ba lang maging taung gumamit king upaya rang mamili
- gamitan ing kabiasnan a mipagkalub karela bang magsilbing kasangkapan ning pamagbayu ning sosiedad. Ampong
- ipagkalub karela ing beluan king teknolohia ampo reng kasanayan  bang maging magamitan a kayanib ning sosiedad/ketawan
